data.description: Welcome to this charming 3 Bedroom home nestled on a corner lot in Neshannock Township.The one-and-a-half-story design adds character to the property, creating a sense of charm and uniqueness. Whether you’re enjoying the convenience of single-floor living or utilizing the additional space on the upper level for a home office, hobby room, or guest quarters, this home offers versatility.
